data.description: This wonderful Liberty Lake style rancher offers 3br/2ba with 2 car garage.  The open kitchen, dining and living area allows enough space to relax while enjoying the warmth of the gas fireplace. You have a front porch and an extended back patio with a 12x12 gazebo. Fully fenced and landscaped backyard, with a 10x20 storage shed. This home won't last. Come take a look today!
